Control node:
[kubes]
kube-01 ansible_host=192.168.1.3 ansible_user=ansible
kube-02 ansible_host=192.168.1.4 ansible_user=ansible
kube-03 ansible_host=192.168.1.5 ansible_user=ansible


[all:vars]
ansible_python_interpreter=/usr/bin/python3

Kubes: 
sætte statisk ip:
network:
  version: 2
  renderer: networkd
  ethernets:
    ens3:
      addresses: [192.168.1.3/24]
      gateway4: 192.168.1.1
      nameservers:
        addresses: [8.8.8.8,8.8.4.4] 

opret ansible user: "sudo adduser ansible" 
derefter give den admin rettigheder: "sudo usermod -aG sudo ansible" 
"sudo visudo" eller "nano /etc/sudoers.tmp" skal du ind i og skrive kommandoen "ansible ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD:ALL" nedenunder "includedir /etc/sudoers.d" for at fjerne kode så du kan opdatere den fra control node
